            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Aesculapio <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Cl<supplied reason="lost">au</supplied>di<lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">anus<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>I <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">aram? signa? et</supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">bas</supplied>es posu<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">it et</supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">m</supplied>armore mu<supplied reason="lost">nivit</supplied> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1-2: Schreibtechnik: appliziert, litterae aureae (in Buchstabenbettungen); erhalten sind nur die Buchstabenbettungen und Dübellöcher im Stein. (B): Z. 3: Schulthess, Meyer: DI nicht gelesen; Finke CLO[---]DI; Z. 4: Walser; Schulthess; Finke: nicht gelesen; Z. 7: Meyer; Schulthess: her]es oder hered]es posu[it oder posu[erunt; Z. 8: Schulthess; Finke: marmorem.</p>
            </div>
